WEBVTT

00:00:28.547 --> 00:00:32.138
never make it to their fifth birthday.

00:00:32.138 --> 00:00:34.594
Most of these deaths are preventable,

00:00:34.594 --> 00:00:36.562
and that doesn't just make me sad,

00:00:36.562 --> 00:00:38.258
it makes me angry,

00:00:38.258 --> 00:00:40.616
and it makes me determined.

00:00:40.616 --> 00:00:42.506
Diarrhea and pneumonia

00:00:42.506 --> 00:00:44.322
are among the top two killers

00:00:44.322 --> 00:00:46.640
of children under five,

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:48.896
and what we can do to prevent these diseases

00:00:48.896 --> 00:00:51.076
isn't some smart,

00:00:51.076 --> 00:00:53.993
new technological innovations.

00:00:53.993 --> 00:00:58.872
It's one of the world's oldest inventions:

00:00:58.872 --> 00:01:02.397
a bar of soap.